cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is primarily focused on deep neural networks and their performance in various tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the theoretical guarantees of the expressivity of the proposed model, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also conducts experiments on a video classification dataset, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed model compared to other models, which falls under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
